</description><media:thumbnail url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/7a511400-4c0f-11eb-9114-005056bfd1d9/w:1024/p:16x9/1fac02d7d5c4578415d9450f53660294f4d3924e.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/7a511400-4c0f-11eb-9114-005056bfd1d9/w:1024/p:16x9/1fac02d7d5c4578415d9450f53660294f4d3924e.jpg" type="image/jpeg" length="0"/><guid isPermaLink="false">0d7880b4-011f-11ec-a58e-005056bf762b</guid><pubDate>Thu, 19 Aug 2021 18:55:39 GMT</pubDate><source url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/7a511400-4c0f-11eb-9114-005056bfd1d9/w:1024/p:16x9/1fac02d7d5c4578415d9450f53660294f4d3924e.jpg">© AFP檔案圖</source><dc:creator>呢喃</dc:creator></item><item><category>亞洲</category><title>阿富汗女記者發視頻求救 指控塔利班已經禁止她工作</title><link>https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2/20210819-%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E5%A5%B3%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E7%99%BC%E8%A6%96%E9%A0%BB%E6%B1%82%E6%95%91-%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E5%A1%94%E5%88%A9%E7%8F%AD%E5%B7%B2%E7%B6%93%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E5%A5%B9%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C</link><description>
