</description><media:thumbnail url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/96027546-00cc-11ec-810d-005056a97e36/w:1024/p:16x9/2021-08-17T143527Z_691021251_RC2Z6P9OVNIR_RTRMADP_3_AFGHANISTAN-CONFLICT.JPG"/><enclosure url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/96027546-00cc-11ec-810d-005056a97e36/w:1024/p:16x9/2021-08-17T143527Z_691021251_RC2Z6P9OVNIR_RTRMADP_3_AFGHANISTAN-CONFLICT.JPG" type="image/jpeg" length="0"/><guid isPermaLink="false">87cf40d4-00cd-11ec-bb17-005056bf762b</guid><pubDate>Thu, 19 Aug 2021 09:12:06 GMT</pubDate><source url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/96027546-00cc-11ec-810d-005056a97e36/w:1024/p:16x9/2021-08-17T143527Z_691021251_RC2Z6P9OVNIR_RTRMADP_3_AFGHANISTAN-CONFLICT.JPG">REUTERS - STRINGER</source><dc:creator>小山</dc:creator></item><item><category>中國</category><title>福建平潭建對台機場</title><link>https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20210819-%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E5%B9%B3%E6%BD%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B0%8D%E5%8F%B0%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4</link><description>
